  <brief_title>Influence of Transcranial Direct Current Stimulation on Cortical Plasticity in Concussed Athletes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Anodal Transcranial Direct Current Stimulation on Cortical Plasticity in Concussed Athletes and Healthy Volunteers</official_title>
